# Amazon Scraping Rules

- CSS selectors live in `config/selectors.yaml` only — never hardcode in scrapers
- Use `safe_goto()` for all page loads; respect REQUEST_DELAY settings
- On captcha/selector failures, append to `.ralph/guardrails.md`
- Run `pytest tests/` after selector changes
- Do not commit `.env` or proxy credentials
